FIT FEB IS HERE 🔥 
The @trainlikeaballerina biggest challenge of the year starts this Monday February 6th! Each year we combine your favorite workouts from all master trainers into one epic challenge. 

🧡 28 days 
🧡 5 workouts per week 
🧡 2 stretching days 
🧡 Barre, floor barre, full body workouts 
🧡 Beginner - Advanced 

How to enroll:
1️⃣ Start your 7-day free trial or login to your TLB App. 
2️⃣ Head to programs & select ‘Fit Feb Challenge 2023’ 
3️⃣ Select MONDAY 6th FEBRUARY as your start date. 
4️⃣ Rest up this weekend because the next 28 days are going to be awesome!
5️⃣ All of your workouts will appear in your personalized calendar on Monday. 

Available exclusively on the TLB App & Web

yesterday, as the curtain came down on ABT’s Fall Season, I took my final bow. Many emotions going on right now, but mostly I am so proud of myself for making this decision and SO excited to begin the next chapter.. pursuing my fitness career full time 💪🏼 I’m so grateful for the wonderful career I had, not just at @abtofficial but also @staatsballettberlin and @bostonballet ❤️ I’m especially grateful for @susanjaffeofficial and her positive leadership, kindness, and respect. Stay tuned for updates on where and how you can start training with me 😈 sending love to my ABT fam.. me and @woof_murphy are ready to kick your 🍑 in the gym when y’all are back from China! ❤️❤️❤️ photo by @yan_revazov_photography #curtaincall #chaptertwo #retirement #conditioningfordancers #ballet #fitness #katieborenfitness #happyplace
